{"tid":1898884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警葵涌邨拘15人稱「老師帶學生犯法」　消息：被捕教師與學生無直接關係","createTime":"2020-02-26T09:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T13:19:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb576997bc705b271c38fbd1a4110026f8fc21a","tid":1898884,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200226/s00001/054715109a1629042e49b085531ef2bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200226%2Fs00001%2F054715109a1629042e49b085531ef2bb.png&h=24dbb5b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（葵青區議員梁錦威facebook片段截圖）<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日（25日）透過facebook短片稱，關注葵涌邨一宗刑毁案中「有老師帶住學生去犯案」，絕不是文明社會接受，呼籲家長及學校多關注年輕人。本報接獲消息稱，被捕的15人中僅一人為教師，任教馬鞍山一間中學，其餘14名被捕者中無一為該校學生，暫未有證據證明他們互相認識。<br />\n<br />\n警方前日（24日）於葵涌邨一平台拘捕8男7女，年齡介乎14至29歲，涉嫌在該處聚集和在牆上張貼海報，並檢獲多張海報和一批膠水，15人涉嫌刑事毁壞被捕。<br />\n<br />\n葵青區議員梁錦威表示，被捕的8男7女中，7名女子已先後獲保釋，而其餘8名男子則選擇拒絕保釋，預計最快於今晚（26日）得知會否被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200226/s00001/1582704381599/%E8%AD%A6%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E9%82%A8%E6%8B%9815%E4%BA%BA%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%B8%B6%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8D-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%88%87%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200226%2Fs00001%2F1582704381599%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%258B%259815%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X0uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=cd87812c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200226%2Fs00001%2F1582704381599%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%2591%25B5%25E6%25B6%258C%25E9%2582%25A8%25E6%258B%259815%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E3%2580%258C%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25B3%2595%25E3%2580%258D-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%258E%25A5%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582&h=d5646fb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200226/s00001/1582704381599/%E8%AD%A6%E8%91%B5%E6%B6%8C%E9%82%A8%E6%8B%9815%E4%BA%BA%E7%A8%B1%E3%80%8C%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%B8%B6%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%8A%AF%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8D-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E8%88%87%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82</a>"},{"pid":"8c01302a3f9a3649a8c79c62671c6702ff1fc2ca","tid":1898884,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:36:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/12134500/image1576129472411.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F12134500%2Fimage1576129472411.png&h=1076db3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7bc70939fab2cca83c461ac85a1c7a23d33567f","tid":1898884,"uid":14918,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:38:10.000Z","msg":"而其餘8名男子則選擇拒絕保釋，預計最快於今晚（26日）得知會否被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n加油, 踢佢老母保"},{"pid":"691b5bbb55eba05b31130406f9130bdee6790ce1","tid":1898884,"uid":6497,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d7bc70939fab2cca83c461ac85a1c7a23d33567f","tid":1898884,"uid":14918,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":1